comments: Nembhard (IND) and Murray (DEN) briefly engage and disengage off-ball.
Turner (IND) turns slightly towards Jokic's (DEN) body as he moves along his path, and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Turner (IND) legally contests Jokic's (DEN) shot near the rim.
Jokic (DEN) clamps and holds Turner's (IND) arm and affects his ability to pursue the rebound.
Turner (IND) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to the Nuggets.
Nembhard (IND) pulls Jokic's (DEN) jersey away from his body and affects his FOM off ball.
Nembhard (IND) brings his forearm forward towards Murray's (DEN) side and marginal contact occurs as they pursue the rebound.
Turner (IND) steps slightly forward towards Murray's (DEN) path and some foot to foot contact occurs as the defenders switch.
Haliburton (IND) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two steps before releasing the jump shot attempt.
Murray (DEN) establishes his left foot as his pivot foot and he slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Turner (IND) legally contests Jokic's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
Turner (IND) brings his arm towards Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) front and marginal contact occurs as Turner releases away for the rebound.
Mathurin (IND) is moving alongside Murray's (DEN) path and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
All Technical Fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Brown (DEN) briefly rest his forearm on Haliburton's (IND) side before correcting, and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Hield (IND) brushes Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) left arm while he reaches at the ball, and the contact is marginal.
Mathurin (IND) swipes his arm down and makes contact with Jokic's (DEN) arm that affects his shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) avoids making body contact with Turner (IND) as he contests the jump shot attempt.
